# ── Adobe CEP carbon copy — keep only the Intricate-specific source ──────
# Premiere loads the LIVE extension from %APPDATA%\Adobe\CEP\... ; the tree
# under ./Adobe/CEP/ is a filing-only copy. Anything that's a build
# artefact, a third-party dependency rehydratable via npm, an Adobe-shipped
# helper, or a secret never lives in the repo.
Adobe/CEP/extensions/com.intricate.bridge/node_modules/
Adobe/CEP/extensions/com.intricate.bridge/META-INF/
Adobe/CEP/extensions/com.intricate.bridge/lib/
Adobe/CEP/extensions/com.intricate.bridge/mimetype
Adobe/CEP/_intricate_signing/*.p12
Adobe/CEP/_intricate_signing/*.zxp
Adobe/CEP/_intricate_signing/ZXPSignCmd.exe